Program: Outlook
Title: Outlook Weekend: The Power of Things
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p045cb3v
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 29 Aug 2016
Three stories about the surprising power of objects: Zachariah Fike returns lost war medals, often antiques, to the families of the soldiers they were awarded to. Nedra Bonds from Missouri has made a name for herself with her very unusual take on political protest - when she is angry about something, she sews a quilt. When Norwegian journalist, Anders Fjellberg heard about a strange object that washed up on a beach in Norway he was determined to find who it had belonged to. Show less